@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>
        <strong>Effective Date:</strong> 11/29/2023
    </p>

    <p>
        Thank you for choosing MusicShop.com, an online service dedicated to providing vocal and instrumental music to customers who enjoy singing or playing instruments. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices concerning the collection, use, and protection of your personal information when you use our website.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect:</h2>

    <p>
        We collect the following types of information to enhance your experience on MusicShop.com:
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> When you create an account, place an order, or engage with our services, we may collect personal information such as your name, email address, billing address, and payment details.</li>

        <li><strong>Music Preferences:</strong> On the "Browse Music" web page, we collect information about your music preferences, including the genre of music you select from the drop-down list.</li>

        <li><strong>Transaction Information:</strong> We collect information about your purchases, including the songs added to your shopping cart and the details of your orders.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information:</h2>

    <p>
        We use the collected information for the following purposes:
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Providing Services:</strong> To deliver the music browsing and shopping experience, including displaying performers, musicians, and groups matching your selected genre.</li>

        <li><strong>Order Processing:</strong> To process and fulfill your orders, including adding selected songs to your shopping cart and facilitating secure payments.</li>

        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> To communicate with you regarding your orders, account information, and important updates related to MusicShop.com.</li>

        <li><strong>Improving Services:</strong> To analyze customer preferences and feedback, helping us enhance our services, user experience, and product offerings.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Security:</h2>

    <p>
        We take the security of your personal information seriously. We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Sharing of Information:</h2>

    <p>
        We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except for the purpose of delivering our services (e.g., payment processing, order fulfillment). We may share aggregated, non-personally identifiable information for analytical purposes.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Your Choices:</h2>

    <p>
        You have the right to control your personal information. You can update your account details, manage communication preferences, and opt-out of promotional emails. You may also request the deletion of your account and associated data.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Cookies and Tracking Technologies:</h2>

    <p>
        We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your browsing experience, analyze usage patterns, and personalize content. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Children's Privacy:</h2>

    <p>
        MusicShop.com is not directed to individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you are a parent or guardian and become aware that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will take steps to delete such information.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Changes to the Privacy Policy:</h2>

    <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the updated policy on our website.
    </p>

    <h2>9. Contact Us:</h2>

    <p>
        If you have questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at musicshop@gmail.com.
    </p>

    <p>
        <strong>By using MusicShop.com, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.</strong>
    </p>
</body>
</html>
